<item>
            <title>[LU-873] IOR single shared file test fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-873</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;IOR fails when &amp;gt; 10 clients are run.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;0289: ERROR in aiori-POSIX.c (line 256): transfer failed.&lt;br/&gt;
0289: ERROR: Input/output error&lt;br/&gt;
0289: ** exiting **&lt;br/&gt;
0289: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;289&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;MPI Abort by user&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Aborting Program!&lt;br/&gt;
0289: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;289:hyperion355&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Abort: MPI_Abort() code: -1, rank 289, MPI Abort by user Aborting program ! at line 99 in file mpid_init.c&lt;br/&gt;
